      <summary>How should I store these gummies?</summary>
      <p>
        Store in a cool, dry place away from direct sunlight. Keep out of reach of children and pets. Reseal package after opening. Do not refrigerate unless specified on packaging.
      </p>
    </details>
    {%- endif -%}
    
    <details>
